item.title: Ajay Kumar S
item.description: About me Hello All, I’m Ajay. I create educational content in TechPrimers. I started this channel on Feb 11, 2017 with the idea to Learn, Code and Share knowledge on the latest technology trends. Since then I have learnt, written and shared lots of code in Github. This repository/github page is dedicated to you all. If you have not contributed to Open Source before, then this is your chance to contribute.
